# ManageSession.intent , MVP Customer Portal / Identity and Access

mission ManageSession

goal
  Issue, refresh, and revoke customer sessions safely.

why
  A session that never expires or cannot be revoked turns one stolen token into
  permanent access.

input
  session: SessionToken

output
  result: SessionState

constraints
  session.ttl <= 24 hours

guarantees
  sessions expire
  revoked sessions cannot be reused

never
  log(session)

verify
  test expired session is rejected
